item.title: By: Nate Eagle
item.dc:creator: Nate Eagle
item.description: You were missed, man. But senior year is exciting: so much happening all the time as you enjoy some of the best parts of school while gearing up for the first really independent phase of your life. Enjoy it as much as you can, don't stress about too much, and come visit your go friends if you get a chance.
